		<title>Lídia Jorge &#8211; &#8220;Para Sophia&#8221;</title>
		<link>http://www.estudioraposa.com/index.php/09/02/2012/lidia-jorge-para-sophia/</link>
		<comments>http://www.estudioraposa.com/index.php/09/02/2012/lidia-jorge-para-sophia/#comments</comments>
